---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About | Miloua Mokhtar">
  <div
    class="dark:bg-stone-700 dark:border-stone-600 2xl:w-1/2 lg:w-[798px] m-auto bg-white border shadow my-4 rounded-md px-2"
  >
    <div class="text-2xl text-center my-6">
      Hi again! I am a web developer from Algeria, sometimes working on the
      frontend, sometimes fullstack. To build my projects, i use
      <b
        ><a
          href="https://nextjs.org/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
          class="transition-colors dark:hover:text-stone-300 hover:text-muted-foreground"
          >Next.js</a
        ></b
      > for fullstack apps, <b
        ><a
          href="https://astro.build/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
          class="transition-colors dark:hover:text-stone-300 hover:text-muted-foreground"
          >Astro</a
        ></b
      > to create content-driven websites, <b
        ><a
          href="https://expo.dev/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
          class="transition-colors dark:hover:text-stone-300 hover:text-muted-foreground"
          >Expo</a
        ></b
      > for mobile development and style everything with <b
        ><a
          href="https://tailwindcss.com/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
          class="transition-colors dark:hover:text-stone-300 hover:text-muted-foreground"
          >Tailwind</a
        ></b
      >. I am mostly into classical <a
        href="/bookshelf"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer"
        class="font-semibold cursor-book color-transition dark:hover:text-stone-300 hover:text-muted-foreground"
        >books</a
      >, enjoy <a
        class="font-semibold cursor-zeus color-transition dark:hover:text-stone-300 hover:text-muted-foreground"
        href="/philosophy"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer">philosophy</a
      >, was addicted to <a
        class="font-semibold cursor-knight color-transition dark:hover:text-stone-300 hover:text-muted-foreground"
        href="https://www.chess.com/member/astroboi21"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer">chess</a
      >, indie <a
        class="font-semibold cursor-ship color-transition dark:hover:text-stone-300 hover:text-muted-foreground"
        href="https://volt.fm/astroboi99"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer">music</a
      > fan and retro video games enjoyer.
    </div>
    <div class="text-center text-xl">
      You can find me on <b class="hover:underline"
        ><a href="https://github.com/Miloua91" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"
          >GitHub</a
        ></b
      >, <b class="hover:underline"
        ><a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mokhtar-miloua/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer">LinkedIn</a
        ></b
      > or DM me on <b class="hover:underline"
        ><a
          href="https://www.instagram.com/miloua191"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer">Instagram</a
        ></b
      >.
    </div>
    <div
      class="dark:bg-stone-600 dark:border-stone-500 2xl:w-[90%] m-auto lg:w-[740px] bg-stone-50 my-4 border border-s-gray-300 px-2 rounded-md"
    >
      <!-- Item #1 -->
      <div class="relative pl-8 sm:pl-32 py-6 group">
        <!-- Purple label -->
        <h1
          class="font-caveat font-medium text-2xl dark:text-purple-200 text-purple-700 mb-1 sm:mb-0"
        >
          Bac Génie Électrique
        </h1>
        <!-- Vertical line (::before) ~ Date ~ Title ~ Circle marker (::after) -->
        <div
          class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start mb-1 group-last:before:hidden before:absolute before:left-2 sm:before:left-0 before:h-full before:px-px before:bg-slate-300 sm:before:ml-[6.5rem] before:self-start before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-3 after:absolute after:left-2 sm:after:left-0 after:w-2 after:h-2 after:bg-purple-400 after:border-4 after:box-content after:border-slate-50 after:rounded-full sm:after:ml-[6.5rem] after:-translate-x-1/2 after:translate-y-1.5"
        >
          <time
            class="sm:absolute left-0 translate-y-0.5 inline-flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-semibold uppercase w-20 h-6 mb-3 sm:mb-0 text-emerald-700 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full"
            >Juin, 2017</time
          >
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold dark:text-slate-200 text-slate-900">
            Amir Khaled, Mascara, Algeria
          </h2>
        </div>
        <!-- Content -->
        <p class="dark:text-slate-100 text-slate-800 text-lg">
          Graduated from high school with a specialization in electrical
          engineering.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Item #2 -->
      <div class="relative pl-8 sm:pl-32 py-6 group">
        <!-- Purple label -->
        <h1
          class="font-caveat font-medium text-2xl dark:text-purple-200 text-purple-700 mb-1 sm:mb-0"
        >
          Master Télécommunication Spatiale
        </h1>
        <!-- Vertical line (::before) ~ Date ~ Title ~ Circle marker (::after) -->
        <div
          class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start mb-1 group-last:before:hidden before:absolute before:left-2 sm:before:left-0 before:h-full before:px-px before:bg-slate-300 sm:before:ml-[6.5rem] before:self-start before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-3 after:absolute after:left-2 sm:after:left-0 after:w-2 after:h-2 after:bg-purple-400 after:border-4 after:box-content after:border-slate-50 after:rounded-full sm:after:ml-[6.5rem] after:-translate-x-1/2 after:translate-y-1.5"
        >
          <time
            class="sm:absolute left-0 translate-y-0.5 inline-flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-semibold uppercase w-20 h-6 mb-3 sm:mb-0 text-emerald-700 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full"
            >Juin, 2023</time
          >
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold dark:text-slate-200 text-slate-900">
            Saad Dahleb University, Blida, Algeria
          </h2>
        </div>
        <!-- Content -->
        <p class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 text-lg">
          The courses I took primarily focused on wired and wireless
          telecommunications, orbital mechanics, and programming.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 text-lg">
          <span class="font-bold">Published conference paper:</span> A UAV-Based
          Close Monitoring of The Vegetation for Precision Agriculture Purposes.
          DOI: <a
            href="https://doi.org/10.1109/M2GARSS57310.2024.10537513"
            target="_blank"
            class="font-bold break-all">10.1109/M2GARSS57310.2024.10537513</a
          >
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Item #3 -->
      <div class="relative pl-8 sm:pl-32 py-6 group">
        <!-- Purple label -->
        <h1
          class="font-caveat font-medium text-2xl dark:text-purple-200 text-purple-700 mb-1 sm:mb-0"
        >
          Web Development
        </h1>
        <!-- Vertical line (::before) ~ Date ~ Title ~ Circle marker (::after) -->
        <div
          class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start mb-1 group-last:before:hidden before:absolute before:left-2 sm:before:left-0 before:h-full before:px-px before:bg-slate-300 sm:before:ml-[6.5rem] before:self-start before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-3 after:absolute after:left-2 sm:after:left-0 after:w-2 after:h-2 after:bg-purple-400 after:border-4 after:box-content after:border-slate-50 after:rounded-full sm:after:ml-[6.5rem] after:-translate-x-1/2 after:translate-y-1.5"
        >
          <time
            class="sm:absolute left-0 translate-y-0.5 inline-flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-semibold uppercase w-20 h-6 mb-3 sm:mb-0 text-emerald-700 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full"
            >August, 2023</time
          >
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold dark:text-slate-200 text-slate-900">
            Self Taught
          </h2>
        </div>
        <!-- Content -->
        <p class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 text-lg">
          After graduating from university, I began learning web development
          with a focus on the frontend. I learned the basics of HTML, CSS, and
          JavaScript, and I am currently working with React and Next.js.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Item #4 -->
      <div class="relative pl-8 sm:pl-32 py-6 group">
        <!-- Purple label -->
        <h1
          class="font-caveat font-medium text-2xl dark:text-blue-200 text-blue-700 mb-1 sm:mb-0"
        >
          Frontend Developer Internship
        </h1>
        <!-- Vertical line (::before) ~ Date ~ Title ~ Circle marker (::after) -->
        <div
          class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start mb-1 group-last:before:hidden before:absolute before:left-2 sm:before:left-0 before:h-full before:px-px before:bg-slate-300 sm:before:ml-[6.5rem] before:self-start before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-3 after:absolute after:left-2 sm:after:left-0 after:w-2 after:h-2 after:bg-blue-400 after:border-4 after:box-content after:border-slate-50 after:rounded-full sm:after:ml-[6.5rem] after:-translate-x-1/2 after:translate-y-1.5"
        >
          <time
            class="sm:absolute left-0 translate-y-0.5 inline-flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-semibold uppercase w-20 h-6 mb-3 sm:mb-0 text-emerald-700 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full"
            >Jun - Sep, 2024</time
          >
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold dark:text-slate-200 text-slate-900">
            <a href="https://alfec.net" target="_blank">Alfec</a>, Oran, Algeria
          </h2>
        </div>
        <!-- Content -->
        <p class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 text-lg">
          First internship after learning web development. My initial tasks were
          to fix bugs in a React Native app and prepare it for cross platform
          publishing. Later, I worked on various projects for their clients,
          including websites and ad panels.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
